</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">overview</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Spend a week living in a surfer's paradise — Bali"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Spend a week </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">living in a surfer's </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line3-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line3" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">paradise — <span class="heading-accent"></span><span class="heading-accent">Bali</span></div></div></h2></div><div class="tag-list"><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Perfect Swells</div></div><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Warm Waters</div></div><div class="tag-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Surf Culture</div></div></div><p>Bali has drawn surfers since the 70s: a legendary destination with waves for every level. Surf every day, explore the island, and connect with people from all around the world. This is the kind of trip that stays with you long after you leave.</p></div><a aria-label="Join the camp – overview" id="w-node-b0ddc51f-e61c-3f56-ff0b-73b1f03337b1-f2b4ae30" data-w-id="b0ddc51f-e61c-3f56-ff0b-73b1f03337b1" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div id="w-node-de33da80-e37b-1289-5944-ecab6d664fa7-f2b4ae30" class="w-layout-grid overview-body"><div id="w-node-_4ef50234-6607-ca98-5d4f-7d69c383a709-f2b4ae30" class="overview-details"><div class="overview-detail"><div class="u-text-color-muted">Where</div><div><strong>Bali, Canggu</strong></div></div><div class="overview-detail"><div class="u-text-color-muted">When</div><div><strong>18 May – 26 May</strong></div></div><div class="overview-detail"><div class="u-text-color-muted">For whom</div><div><strong>All Skill Levels</strong></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_4ef50234-6607-ca98-5d4f-7d69c383a6d4-f2b4ae30" class="slider-wrap"><div data-delay="10000" data-animation="slide" class="slider is-overview w-slider" data-autoplay="true" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="5