-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>Never been on a board? We'll start with the basics on the beach — how to pop up, read the waves, and stay safe. Your first ride will happen sooner than you think.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee37-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfboard-feet-action.webp" loading="lazy"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>beginner</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Still Learning</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You've surfed a few times and can catch some white water. We'll help you progress to green waves and work on your technique in a supportive environment.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee49-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/man-surfing-wave.webp" loading="lazy"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>intermediate</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Pretty Confident</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You're catching waves regularly and want to improve your style. We'll take you to better breaks and help you level up your skills with the group.</p></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_94ea0941-3c75-c816-7244-83836e27ee5b-f2b4ae30" class="levels-card"><div class="u-flex-row"><div class="image-circle-wrap"><img width="80" height="80" alt="" src="/assets/img/shaka-hand.webp" loading="lazy"></div><div class="badge" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><div>advanced</div></div></div><div class="levels-card-content"><div class="levels-card-header"><h3>Already a Pro</h3><div class="chevron-button is-hidden-desktop"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="levels-card-body" style="height: 0px"><div class="line-spacer-wrap"><div class="line-base"></div></div><p>You know what you're doing out there. Come surf the best spots with us, share tips with others, and enjoy the crew without needing instruction.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-stay" class="section-stay"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div id="w-node-_5749e172-c283-2744-41d4-11c2c60d747f-f2b4ae30" class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="layout-stack"><div class="w-layout-grid stay-header"><div id="w-node-_5749e172-c283-2744-41d4-11c2c60d7482-f2b4ae30" class="heading-wrap is-small"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
