63-f2b4ae30" class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for body</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Yoga and Meditation</h3><p>Stretch out your surf-tired muscles with sunset yoga and start your mornings centered with guided meditation sessions.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/waterfall.avif" loading="lazy" class="emoji"></div></div><div id="w-node-_309f40c5-e3b5-1b6c-5dea-79914643a66f-f2b4ae30" class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for soul</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Temples and Ceremonies</h3><p>Experience Bali's spiritual side through ancient temple visits and evening circles where we share what really matters.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/villa.avif" loading="lazy" class="emoji"></div></div><div class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for mind</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Culture and Growth </h3><p>Learn the stories behind the island at local markets and connect over dinners designed for real conversation.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfing.avif" loading="lazy" class="emoji"></div></div><div class="experience-card"><div class="experience-card-content-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">for fun</div><div class="experience-card-text"><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Adventures Together</h3><p>Discover hidden beaches on scooters, eat your way through night markets, and stay up late swapping travel stories.</p></div></div><div class="emoji-wrap"><img width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/surfers.avif" loading="lazy" class="emoji"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-cta-1