div class="day-pane-text"><p>Your first proper day! We'll ease you into Bali surf with a morning session at a beginner-friendly break. Instructors will assess everyone's level and split into groups so you're with people at your pace. In the afternoon, we explore Canggu on scooters to get our bearings. Tonight we'll hit up a local warung for authentic Balinese food.<br></p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 2" data-w-id="409a8475-a7ca-baca-c664-cab6ddbee788" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img width="928" height="1232" alt="Two women in swimwear carrying surfboards while walking across a lush green lawn through a grove of palm trees toward the beach." src="/assets/img/surfers-palm-garden.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-1-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-1-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:00-07:30</div></div><div>Wake up call</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:30-08:30 </div></div><div>Breakfast at villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-09:00 </div></div><div>Transport to surf spot</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>09:00-09:45</div></div><div>Beach theory session (surf basics, safety)</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>09:45-11:30 </div></div><div>First surf session in the water</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>11:30-12:00 </div></div><div>Transport back to villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>12:00-13:00 </div></div><div>Shower and change</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>13:00-14:00</div></div><div>Lunch at beach café</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>14:00-14:30 </div></div><div>Scooter safety briefing</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>14:30-17:30 </div></div><div>Guided scooter tour of Canggu</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>17:30-18:30 </div></div><div>Back at villa, free time</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>18:30-19:30 </div></div><div>Sunset yoga session at villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:30-20:00 </div></div><div>Freshen up</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>20:00-21:30 </div></div><div>Dinner at local warung</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:30-23:00</div></div><div>Evening walk or villa hangout</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-06:30</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 3</div><h3>Surf Progress &amp; Beach Club</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-d