rdion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 5<br></div><h3>Surf &amp; Waterfall Adventure</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img width="900" height="1201" alt="Group of friends standing on rocks in front of a tall tropical waterfall." src="/assets/img/waterfall-group.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-e974dbab-9637-f051-10a0-f5145c7f9fae-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-4-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-4-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-e974dbab-9637-f051-10a0-f5145c7f9fb5-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-4-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>Back in the water! Morning session at a new spot — slightly more challenging waves for those ready, or continued practice at the mellow break. In the afternoon, we head to a hidden waterfall. Bring your GoPro — this is one of those Bali moments you'll want to remember. Tonight, cook together at the villa.</p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 5" data-w-id="390b9d66-9387-8ee6-85d5-e488dafdf9e5" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img width="900" height="1201" alt="Group of friends standing on rocks in front of a tall tropical waterfall." src="/assets/img/waterfall-group.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-4-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-4-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>06:30-07:00</div></div><div>Wake up</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:00-08:00 </div></div><div>Breakfast</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:00-08:30 </div></div><div>Transport to new surf spot</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-11:30 </div></div><div>Surf session</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>11:30-12:00 </div></div><div>Transport back to villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>12:00-13:00</div></div><div>Quick shower and change</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>13:00-13:30 </div></div><div>Packed lunch at villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>13:30-14:30 </div></div><div>Drive to waterfall<br></div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>14:30-16:30 </div></div><div>Waterfall hike and swim</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>16:30-17:30 </div></div><div>Drive back to villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>17:30-18:30 </div></div><div>Shower and rest</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>18:30-19:00 </div></div><div>Grocery shopping for dinner</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:00-20:30 </div></div><div>Cook dinner together at villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>20:30-21:30 </div></div><div>Dinner</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:30-23:00 </div></div><div>Card games and rooftop talks</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-07:00</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 6<br></div><h3>Surf &amp; Spa Day</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img width="928" height="1232" alt="A woman relaxing in a steaming natural stone hot tub outdoors, surrounded by sunlit trees and dense forest greenery." src="/assets/img/outdoor-spa-forest.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-_2621f860-64ed-30bf-527c-b55f2020426d-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-5-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-5-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-5-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-5-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-5-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-5-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-_2621f860-64ed-30bf-527c-b55f20204274-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-5-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-5-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>Morning surf — by now you're feeling the rhythm of the ocean. This afternoon is all about self-care. We've arranged group rates at a local spa for massages. Tonight we're going out — live music at a beach bar, dancing, and celebrating the week.</p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 6" data-w-id="a5e17e5b-9637-a82d-531f-f3d7d1f0a966" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24"