y-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>18:00-19:00</div></div><div>Sunset drinks at villa</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:00-20:00</div></div><div>Get ready for night out</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>20:00-21:00</div></div><div>Dinner at restaurant</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:00-22:00</div></div><div>Beach bar with live music and dancing</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>22:00-23:00</div></div><div>Late night snacks or continue partying</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-06:30</div></div><div>Back to villa and sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion"><div class="day-accordion-header"><div class="day-header-content"><div class="day-heading-wrap"><div class="eyebrow-item">Day 7<br></div><h3>Final Surf &amp; Farewell </h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="follow-cursor-wrap" style="display: flex"><div class="follow-cursor"><img width="900" height="1200" alt="Four people sitting on grass in a circle with four surfboards standing upright against tropical greenery behind them." src="/assets/img/surfers-circle.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="line-fill-wrap"><div class="line-fill-color"></div><div class="line-base u-absolute-full"></div></div></div><div class="day-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="day-tabs-wrap"><div data-current="Tab 1" data-easing="ease" data-duration-in="300" data-duration-out="100" class="day-tabs-parent w-tabs"><div id="w-node-e09e26d0-0a27-4037-c1f9-0e2f1de7f6c8-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-menu w-tab-menu" role="tablist"><a data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current" id="w-tabs-6-data-w-tab-0" href="#w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-0" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-0" aria-selected="true"><div>Description</div></a><a data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link" tabindex="-1" id="w-tabs-6-data-w-tab-1" href="#w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-1" role="tab" aria-controls="w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-1" aria-selected="false"><div>Timetable</div></a></div><div id="w-node-e09e26d0-0a27-4037-c1f9-0e2f1de7f6cf-f2b4ae30" class="day-tabs-content w-tab-content"><div data-w-tab="Tab 1" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active" id="w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-0" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-6-data-w-tab-0"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-pane-text"><p>Last surf of the week—make it count! This morning is bittersweet as you catch your final waves with the crew. Afternoon is open for last-minute shopping or beach time. Tonight we gather for a farewell dinner, share highlights, exchange contacts, and probably get a little emotional. If you're staying for Week 2, this is just halftime!</p><a aria-label="Join the camp – day 7" data-w-id="ed137b64-2bf7-988d-c2ec-3f8ef7ea9790" href="#" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Join The Camp</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div><div class="day-pane-image"><img width="900" height="1200" alt="Four people sitting on grass in a circle with four surfboards standing upright against tropical greenery behind them." src="/assets/img/surfers-circle.avif" loading="lazy"></div></div></div><div data-w-tab="Tab 2" class="day-tab-pane w-tab-pane" id="w-tabs-6-data-w-pane-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="w-tabs-6-data-w-tab-1"><div class="day-pane-content-wrap"><div class="day-timetable"><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>06:30-07:00</div></div><div>Wake up</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>07:00-08:00 </div></div><div>Breakfast</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:00-08:30 </div></div><div>Transport to surf spot</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>08:30-11:30 </div></div><div>Final surf session </div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>11:30-12:00 </div></div><div>Group photo at the beach</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>12:00-13:00</div></div><div>Lunch at beach café</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>13:00-15:00 </div></div><div>Last-minute shopping in Canggu</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>15:00-18:00 </div></div><div>Beach time or packing </div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>18:00-19:00 </div></div><div>Shower and get ready</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>19:00-21:30 </div></div><div>Farewell dinner at special restaurant</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>21:30-23:00 </div></div><div>Bonfire at the beach, sharing highlights</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>23:00-01:00 </div></div><div>Final night music and memories</div></div><div class="day-timetable-item"><div class="timetable-time"><div>01:00-07:00</div></div><div>Sleep</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-instructors" class="section-instructors"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid layout-grid"><div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cd9b-f2b4ae30" class="slider-wrap"><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider is-instructors w-slider" data-autoplay="false" data-easing="ease" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true" role="region" aria-label="carousel"><div class="w-slider-mask" id="w-slider-mask-1"><div class="slide is-instructors w-slide" aria-label="1 of 2" role="group" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img src="/assets/img/5010 1.webp" loading="lazy" width="940" height="854" alt="A smiling professional surf instructor in a black wetsuit holding a white surfboard against a lush tropical jungle background." srcset="/assets/img/5010 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/5010 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/5010 1-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/img/5010 1.webp 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px"></div><div class="slide-content"><div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content"><div class="slide-popup-heading">Wayan Bayu</div><div>I was born and raised right here on Bali's coast – I've been surfing these breaks since I was five years old. Teaching surfing is more than just a job for me — it's sharing my home and my culture with you. I love watching beginners catch their first wave, that moment when everything clicks and you feel the ocean carry you. <br><br>Whether you're standing up for the first time or working on advanced maneuvers, I'll be right there in the water with you, making sure you're safe, having fun, and actually improving. My goal is simple: by the end of camp, you'll surf better and understand the ocean better.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Coach: Wayan Bayu</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost"><div class="plus-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>ENG / IND</div></div></div></div></div><div data-w-id="43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdb5" class="slide is-instructors w-slide" aria-label="2 of 2" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img src="/assets/img/surf-coach-02.webp" loading="lazy" width="1360" height="1237" alt="A portrait of a friendly man in a wetsuit posing with his surfboard in front of vibrant green palm leaves." srcset="/assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02-p-1080.webp 1080w, /assets/img/surf-coach-02.webp 1360w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Finn O'Brien</div><div aria-hidden="true">I'm from the Gold Coast originally – grew up surfing Snapper Rocks and Burleigh. Came to Bali for a two-week surf trip about seven years ago and just... never went home. The waves here are incredible, but honestly, it's the people and the lifestyle that got me. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">I started coaching because I saw so many tourists getting terrible advice from random guys on the beach. I wanted to actually teach people properly – ocean safety, reading conditions, real technique. Whether you're catching your first wave or trying to nail a cutback, I'll break it down for you step by step. My job is to get you surfing better and keep you stoked the whole time.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Coach: Finn O'Brien </div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">ENG / IND / ESP</div></div></div></div></div><div aria-live="off" aria-atomic="true" class="w-slider-aria-label" data-wf-ignore=""></div></div><div class="left-arrow is-frost-on-image u-absolute-bottom-right w-slider-arrow-left" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-1" aria-label="previous slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="right-arrow is-frost-on-image u-absolute-bottom-right w-slider-arrow-right" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-1" aria-label="next slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="slide-nav is-hidden w-slider-nav"><div class="w-slider-dot w-active" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 1 of 2" aria-pressed="true" role="button" tabindex="0" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 2 of 2" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div></div></div></div><div id="w-node-_43e575a5-747b-91e3-85a8-60a43d77cdd1-f2b4ae30" class="heading-wrap is-small"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
