ctors hold international surf certification with 5+ years teaching experience.</p></div><div class="instructors-benefit"><div class="thumbs-up-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-thumbs-up-icon lucide-thumbs-up"><path d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"></path><path d="M7 10v12"></path></svg></div><div><strong>Small Group Focus</strong></div><p>Max 6 people per instructor. Personalized feedback, proper supervision, faster progression.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-testimonials" class="section-testimonials"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="layout-split"><div id="w-node-_0abc99a5-fbf2-bb70-fee3-442e2506339a-f2b4ae30" class="testimonials-header"><div class="title-wrap"><div class="heading-wrap is-small"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
