="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Travel and medical insurance</div></div><div class="pricing-feature-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Personal expenses and shopping</div></div><div class="pricing-feature-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Activities outside the camp program</div></div><div class="pricing-feature-item"><div class="check-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check-icon lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg></div><div>Lunches (usually $5–12 at local spots)</div></div></div></nav></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-faq" class="section-faq"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="w-layout-grid layout-grid"><div id="w-node-d6f01f14-e0ce-c614-6967-f40477c67f10-f2b4ae30" class="heading-wrap"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M7.24994 2.5V4.64746L9.289 3.98437C9.94554 3.77105 10.6508 4.13058 10.8642 4.78711C11.0775 5.44356 10.7188 6.14883 10.0624 6.3623L8.01849 7.02637L9.28119 8.76562C9.68687 9.3242 9.5634 10.106 9.00482 10.5117C8.44625 10.9173 7.66437 10.7929 7.25872 10.2344L5.99603 8.49609L4.73333 10.2324C4.32753 10.7908 3.54571 10.9145 2.98724 10.5088C2.42881 10.103 2.30511 9.32117 2.71087 8.76269L3.97454 7.02539L1.93451 6.3623C1.27801 6.14897 0.918527 5.44363 1.13177 4.78711C1.34508 4.13061 2.05046 3.77119 2.70697 3.98437L4.74994 4.64844V2.5C4.74994 1.8098 5.3098 1.25026 5.99994 1.25C6.69029 1.25 7.24994 1.80964 7.24994 2.5Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">faq</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Frequently </div></div><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line2-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line2" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Asked Questions</div></div></h2></div><div id="w-node-d6f01f14-e0ce-c614-6967-f40477c67f1a-f2b4ae30" class="faq-body"><div class="faq-list"><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">01</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Do I need to know how to surf already?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>Not at all! Most people who come are complete beginners or have only surfed a few times. Our instructors work with all levels, and we split into groups so you're learning with people at your pace. If you can swim and are willing to try, you're ready.</p></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">02</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">I'm traveling alone — will I feel out of place?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>Actually, most people come solo. That's the beauty of it — everyone's in the same boat (or on the same board). By day two, it feels like you've known each other forever. Solo travelers often tell us this was the best decision they made.</p></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">03</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">What's not included in the price?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>Lunches (we usually grab these together at local spots, budget $5–12), personal expenses like extra massages or shopping, travel insurance, and your flight to Bali. Everything else — accommodation, breakfast, dinner, surf lessons, activities, airport transfers — is covered.</p></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">04</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">What if the dates don't work for me?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>We run multiple sessions throughout the year. If these dates don't fit your schedule, drop us a message and we'll let you know when the next camps are happening. You can also join our email list to be the first to know about new dates.</p></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">05</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Is Bali safe for travelers?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes! Bali, especially Canggu, is very safe and welcoming to international travelers. The local community is used to surfers and tourists, and we'll be with you for most activities. We'll also give you a full safety briefing on day one covering everything from scooter riding to ocean awareness.</p></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion"><div class="faq-accordion-header"><div class="faq-question"><div class="eyebrow-item">06</div><h3 class="u-heading-h3-small">Can I extend my stay at the villa?</h3></div><div class="chevron-button"><div class="chevron-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="faq-accordion-body" style="width: 100%; height: 0px"><div class="faq-answer"><p>Sometimes! If the villa isn't booked for another camp immediately after, we can often arrange for you to stay a few extra nights at a discounted rate. Just let us know in advance and we'll check availability. Many people do this to explore Bali on their own after the camp ends.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div id="w-node-d6f01f14-e0ce-c614-6967-f40477c67f6a-f2b4ae30" class="faq-cta-wrap"><div class="emoji-wrap"><img width="50" height="50" alt="" src="/assets/img/hls-44-4YzILMQDQFg-unsplash.avif" loading="lazy" data-wf-target="[[[&quot;697a02e7f32a15a9f2b4ae30&quot;,&quot;d6f01f14-e0ce-c614-6967-f40477c67f6c&quot;],[]]]" class="emoji" style="transform-origin: 100% 100%"></div><div class="faq-cta-content"><h4>Still have questions?</h4><p>Whether it's about the program, accommodation, or anything in between — we're happy to help.</p></div><a data-w-id="5578a3f2-923d-5ba5-f055-45d8988c5027" href="mailto:hello@surfhaven.camp?subject=Tell%20me%20more%20about%20the%20camp!" class="secondary-button w-inline-block"><div>Contact Us</div><div class="arrow-tail-button"><div class="arrow-tail-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-arrow-up-right-icon lucide-arrow-up-right"><path d="M7 7h10v10"></path><path d="M7 17 17 7"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-team" class="section-team"><div class="padding-horizontal"><div class="padding-vertical"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-standard w-container"><div class="layout-stack"><div class="team-header"><div class="heading-wrap"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 12 12" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <path d="M7.24994 2.5V4.64746L9.289 3.98437C9.94554 3.77105 10.6508 4.13058 10.8642 4.78711C11.0775 5.44356 10.7188 6.14883 10.0624 6.3623L8.01849 7.02637L9.28119 8.76562C9.68687 9.3242 9.5634 10.106 9.00482 10.5117C8.44625 10.9173 7.66437 10.7929 7.25872 10.2344L5.99603 8.49609L4.73333 10.2324C4.32753 10.7908 3.54571 10.9145 2.98724 10.5088C2.42881 10.103 2.30511 9.32117 2.71087 8.76269L3.97454 7.02539L1.93451 6.3623C1.27801 6.14897 0.918527 5.44363 1.13177 4.78711C1.34508 4.13061 2.05046 3.77119 2.70697 3.98437L4.74994 4.64844V2.5C4.74994 1.8098 5.3098 1.25026 5.99994 1.25C6.69029 1.25 7.24994 1.80964 7.24994 2.5Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
</svg></div><div class="eyebrow-section">TEAM</div></div><h2 class="heading-h2" aria-label="Meet the team"><div class="gsap_split_line-mask gsap_split_line1-mask" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start; overflow: clip"><div class="gsap_split_line gsap_split_line1" aria-hidden="true" style="position: relative; display: block; text-align: start">Meet the team</div></div></h2></div><p>The ones who planned a surf camp, not a photoshoot</p></div><div id="w-node-_22fe9cd3-bc58-b1f9-ea5d-f6753de580bf-f2b4ae30" class="team-body"><div data-delay="4000" data-animation="slide" class="slider is-team w-slider" data-autoplay="false" data-easing="ease-in-out" data-hide-arrows="false" data-disable-swipe="false" data-autoplay-limit="0" data-nav-spacing="3" data-duration="500" data-infinite="true" role="region" aria-label="carousel"><div class="team-slider-mask w-slider-mask" id="w-slider-mask-3"><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="1 of 5" role="group" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full"><img width="900" height="1232" alt="A man wearing an orange propeller hat and sunglasses, gesturing with his hands in front of large tropical palm leaves." src="/assets/img/Frame 1618873057.webp" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/Frame 1618873057-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/Frame 1618873057-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/Frame 1618873057.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 900px"></div><div class="slide-content"><div class="slide-popup"><div class="slide-popup-content"><div class="slide-popup-heading">Kaspars Liepa</div><div>I want you to spend these days doing something real – catching waves, pushing past your comfort zone, hanging out with people who get it. When I came to Bali years ago, I wasn't looking for anything specific, but surfing here changed how I see things. Not in some cheesy way, just... different. Clearer. <br><br>And the crew here – we all work together to make sure you get the most out of every single day.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Kaspars</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost"><div class="plus-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus"><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="M12 5v14"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right"><div class="badge u-frost"><div>Founder</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="2 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img width="900" height="1232" alt="A smiling woman with long dark hair and facial piercings, holding her hand out toward the camera in a tropical setting." src="/assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR.webp" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/FOYWWNMfi7U46sD9CUBWWApj0NToLyGR.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 900px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Christina Lee</div><div aria-hidden="true">I'm basically living my dream job – I get to hang out at the beach all day, meet amazing people from all over the world, and tell their stories through photos and videos. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">But what I love most is capturing that exact moment when someone stands up on a wave for the first time – the pure joy on their face is unreal. I also run our Instagram and make sure our community stays connected, so don't be shy to tag us in your posts!</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Christina</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">SMM guru</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="3 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img width="900" height="1233" alt="A man with dark hair laughing heartily with his head tilted back, set against a blurred green foliage background." src="/assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u.webp" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/my2u5vmy2u5vmy2u.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 900px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Noah Miller</div><div aria-hidden="true">I'm the guy you'll probably talk to first when you're thinking about joining us, and I promise I'll give it to you straight – no sales pitch, just honest advice about which program fits you best. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">Once you're here, I'm all about making sure everyone feels welcome and the crew energy is right. Whether you need a pep talk before paddling out or just someone to grab a Bintang with after sunset, I've got you. Your experience matters to me, for real.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Noah</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Sales Manager</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="4 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img width="900" height="1233" alt="A man with short curly hair smiling warmly with his arms crossed, wearing a black t-shirt in front of palm trees." src="/assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1.webp" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/6bibjs6bibjs6bib 1.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 900px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Tyler Carter</div><div aria-hidden="true">I know 'logistics' sounds boring, but trust me, it's what makes or breaks your trip. I'm obsessed with the details – making sure your room is ready, the surf spots match the conditions, breakfast is on time, and our drivers know exactly where to be. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">I've been living in Bali for three years now, so I know all the hidden gems and local spots. Basically, I handle all the planning stress so you can just show up and have the best time.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Tyler</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Coordinator</div></div></div></div></div><div class="slide is-team w-slide" aria-label="5 of 5" role="group" aria-hidden="true" style="transition: all"><div class="image-wrap u-absolute-full" aria-hidden="true"><img width="900" height="1200" alt="A woman with short blonde hair winking and making an &quot;OK&quot; hand gesture while smiling in a lush green outdoor environment." src="/assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1.webp" loading="lazy" srcset="/assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1-p-500.webp 500w, /assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1-p-800.webp 800w, /assets/img/ipbnx0ipbnx0ipbn 1.webp 900w" sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 900px" aria-hidden="true"></div><div class="slide-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-content" aria-hidden="true"><div class="slide-popup-heading" aria-hidden="true">Sofia Bergman</div><div aria-hidden="true">I handle all the fun stuff – organizing beach bonfires, planning trips to temples or waterfalls, setting up morning yoga, hosting game nights, you name it. <br aria-hidden="true"><br aria-hidden="true">Camp life is about balance, so while you're pushing yourself in the water, I make sure there's plenty of time to explore Bali, relax, and bond with the group. My goal is to keep the energy high and make sure everyone's having a great time on and off the board.</div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Sofia</div></div><div class="plus-button u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div class="plus-icon w-embed" aria-hidden="true"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-plus-icon lucide-plus" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14" aria-hidden="true"></path><path d="M12 5v14" aria-hidden="true"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="slide-content-meta is-right" aria-hidden="true"><div class="badge u-frost" aria-hidden="true"><div aria-hidden="true">Event Manager</div></div></div></div></div><div aria-live="off" aria-atomic="true" class="w-slider-aria-label" data-wf-ignore=""></div></div><div class="left-arrow u-absolute-top-right is-offset w-slider-arrow-left" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-3" aria-label="previous slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="right-arrow u-absolute-top-right is-offset w-slider-arrow-right" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-controls="w-slider-mask-3" aria-label="next slide"><div class="arrow-icon w-embed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-chevron-down-icon lucide-chevron-down"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path></svg></div></div><div class="slide-nav is-hidden w-slider-nav"><div class="w-slider-dot w-active" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 1 of 5" aria-pressed="true" role="button" tabindex="0" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 2 of 5" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 3 of 5" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 4 of 5" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div><div class="w-slider-dot" data-wf-ignore="" aria-label="Show slide 5 of 5" aria-pressed="false" role="button" tabindex="-1" style="margin-left: 3px; margin-right: 3px"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="popup-form" class="popup-form" style="display: none"><div class="padding-popup"><div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-small w-container"><div class="layout-popup"><div id="w-node-_32c714b9-8c51-3c0f-f735-e2aff119834a-f1198346" class="form-header"><div class="heading-wrap"><div class="icon-eyebrow-group"><div class="star-icon w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 32 32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
